sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as Kueue Controller<br/>kueue-controller-manager
    participant CQ as ClusterQueue
    participant Autoscaler as Cluster Autoscaler

    Note over User,Autoscaler: Flow 1: Job Submission and Admission

    User->>K8sAPI: Submit Job/PyTorchJob/AppWrapper<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Mutating webhook call<br/>mTLS
    Webhook->>Webhook: Add queue labels<br/>Suspend job
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Modified job spec
    K8sAPI-->>User: Job created (suspended)

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch job resources<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>Controller: Create Workload CR<br/>from job spec
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Workload<br/>ServiceAccount Token

    Controller->>CQ: Evaluate queue position<br/>Apply queueing strategy

    alt Resources Available
        Controller->>Controller: Admit workload<br/>Update Workload status
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Unsuspend job<br/>Allow pod creation
        K8sAPI->>K8sAPI: Create pods
        Note over Controller: Job runs to completion
    else Resources Not Available
        Controller->>CQ: Enqueue workload<br/>Wait in queue
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ProvisioningRequest<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        Autoscaler->>K8sAPI: Watch ProvisioningRequest<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        Autoscaler->>Autoscaler: Provision nodes<br/>Cloud Provider API
        Autoscaler->>K8sAPI: Update ProvisioningRequest status
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch ProvisioningRequest updates
        Note over Controller: Retry admission when resources ready
    end

    Note over User,Autoscaler: Flow 2: Metrics Collection

    participant Prometheus as Prometheus
    Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    Controller-->>Prometheus: Queue metrics<br/>admission metrics

    Note over User,Autoscaler: Flow 3: Visibility API Query

    User->>K8sAPI: GET /apis/visibility.kueue.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1/<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS, Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Visibility: Forward request<br/>8082/TCP HTTPS, K8s mTLS
    Visibility->>Visibility: Query queue cache<br/>pending workloads
    Visibility-->>K8sAPI: Workload list
    K8sAPI-->>User: JSON response
